        The noble Lord said: We are talking now about the commutation of periodic compensation. The paragraph starts with what happens under prescribed
        
        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_213gc' title='Col. 213GC &mdash; HL Deb 09 September 2004 vol 664 c213GC' name='column_213gc' href='#column_213gc' rel='bookmark'>213GC</a>
