        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 226 and 227 not moved</span>.]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05102'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040909_GCR_138' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Hollis of Heigham</span> moved Amendment No. 227A:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05103'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040909_GCR_139' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 278, line 38, leave out "under the scheme or another scheme"
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05104'>
