        <li>(c) paragraph 15 as it applies by virtue of paragraph 20,</li>
        </ol>
        which is attributable (directly or indirectly) to a pension credit.</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05153'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040909_GCR_189' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
