      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05351'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040909_GCR_387' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Hollis of Heigham</span> moved Amendment No. 235A:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05352'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040909_GCR_388' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 113, line 2, at end insert "rules"
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-05353'>
