          <p class='first-para'>
            I assume it is meant to refer to a later matter. I just wondered whether there was a slight problem.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-05388'>
        <a name='S5LV0664P0_20040909_GCR_424'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-terence-higgins' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
