        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_259gc' title='Col. 259GC &mdash; HL Deb 09 September 2004 vol 664 c259GC' name='column_259gc' href='#column_259gc' rel='bookmark'>259GC</a>
        there should be an up-rating. I think that we should at least ensure that consultation takes place. To what extent it needs to be approved on a broader basis is a matter for consideration. I beg to move.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-05534'>
